---
title: Apricot Chicken Tenders with Roasted Potatoes
description: The combination of apricot jam and mustard makes a summery and delicious glaze for chicken to brighten up the middle of winter! Roasted potatoes and a bright spring-inspired salad add richness and texture, making every mouthful a taste-experience.
